                     </app>
                     <app type="text">
                        <lem><foreign xml:lang="grc">αὐτὸς γὰρ</foreign></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#C #P5"><foreign xml:lang="grc">αὐτὸς γὰρ ἦν</foreign></rdg>
                        <wit>Coislin 10</wit>
                        <wit>Coislin 12</wit>
                     </app>
                     <app type="text">
                        <lem><foreign xml:lang="grc">ἡ</foreign></lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B1"><foreign xml:lang="grc">ἧ</foreign></rdg>
                        <wit>Auct. D.4.1</wit>
                     </app>
                     <note type="textal-commentary">V1: exp. 508 in the inner (left) column, not in
                        the main text.</note>
                  </div>
                  <div type="psalmtext">
                     <quote type="psalmtext" xml:id="edition-26-30-ps-26-11b" n="11b">καὶ ὁδήγησόν
                        με ἐν τρίβῳ εὐθείᾳ ἕνεκα τῶν ἐχθρῶν μου.</quote>
                  </div>
               </div>
               <div type="translation" xml:lang="de">
                  <quote type="psalmtext" corresp="#edition-26-30-ps-26-11a" n="11a">Gib mir dein
                     Gesetz, Herr, für deinen Weg,</quote>
                  <p corresp="#edition-26-30-26-11-1" n="508">Er fleht, es möge das Gesetz des
                     Evangeliums ihm enthüllt werden. Denn das war der gerade Weg.</p>
                  <quote type="psalmtext" corresp="#edition-26-30-ps-26-11b" n="11b">und führe mich
                     auf geraden Pfad um meiner Feinde willen.</quote>
               </div>
            </div>
            <div type="psalmverse" n="26.12">
               <div type="text" xml:lang="grc">
                  <div type="psalmtext">
                     <quote type="psalmtext" xml:id="edition-26-30-ps-26-12a" n="12a">μὴ παραδῷς με
                        εἰς ψυχὰς θλιβόντων με,</quote>
                     <quote type="psalmtext" xml:id="edition-26-30-ps-26-12b" n="12b">ὅτι
                        ἐπανέστησάν μοι μάρτυρες ἄδικοι,</quote>
                     <quote type="psalmtext" xml:id="edition-26-30-ps-26-12c" n="12c">καὶ ἐψεύσατο ἡ
                        ἀδικία ἑαυτῇ.</quote>
                  </div>
                  <div type="commentary">
                     <p xml:id="edition-26-30-26-12-1" n="509">Τουτέστιν ἠσθένησεν ἡ καθ' ἡμῶν
                        ἀδικία: –</p>
                     <div type="links">
                        <p>
                           <listRef>
                              <ref target="#vat-gr-754:vat-gr-754-fr-26-50"/>
                              <ref target="#coislin-10:coislin-10-fr-26-46"/>
                              <ref target="#franzon-3:franzon-3-fr-26-27"/>
